An application to control a toy car remotely. This car uses an Arduino.
The application has at this moment, 2018/07/28, three main screens:

* List devices. This is a screen that lets the user discover bluetooth devices and connect to them.
* Joystick. Once connected to a device. This is a screen lets the user control the car.
* Settings. This is a screen that lets the user configure some settings. Like the language.

